            "summary": "SLE: Fire - 03-2025 - Fire ",
            "description": "<p>According to the National Disaster Management Agency,a devastating fire incident occured in kptema village Bo district causing extensive damage to homes and livelihoods. The fire completely destroyed 45 houses and 13 rice bans leaving 645 people homeless. The affected families have lost their shelter food supply and essential belongs, increasing their vulnerabilities. The cause of the fire remains unknown and the National Disaster Management Agency and sierra leone red cross society are assessing the situation to determine the level of impact.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>",
